### Register
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vitalik_api@gmail.com",
  "username": "vitalik_test",
  "password": "super_secure_password"
}


### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vitalik_api@gmail.com",
  "password": "super_secure_password"
}


