### Загрузка медиафайла
POST http://localhost:5000/media/upload
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI4YzY4YjVjZS0wZDFkLTQ1YzUtYTdlMS0wZDM4ZGQ0YTA5NjEiLCJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODA2NTEwNDYsImV4cCI6MTc4MDczNzQ0Nn0.H6I0MOiiei-GrYscXnySR5_PiuHgjG1BtqME-oOM3Ns
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My Cool Avatar
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_image.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test_image.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### Получить все публичные медиафайлы
GET http://localhost:5000/media?page=1&limit=5&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI4YzY4YjVjZS0wZDFkLTQ1YzUtYTdlMS0wZDM4ZGQ0YTA5NjEiLCJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODA0Nzk0NzYsImV4cCI6MTc4MDU2NTg3Nn0.F8TyhEY8XG9V3xkz5YK7i19Ie9vkniRUXEkFGoODgmg

